item.title: Kerrang! Back Issues S03E23 No: 600 June 8 1996
item.description:
Issue no: 600. June 8 1996. This week we talk about Bon Jovi, Def leppard, Reef, Metallica, Bush, Everclear, Hum, Feeder, Manic Street Preachers, Cannibal Corpse, Euro '96, Rancid, Biohazard, Carcass, Sense Field, Avail, No Doubt, plus all of the regulars including feedback, lives, albums, news, and much more.

item.title: This Month in German, Swiss, and Austrian (GSA) Startups?-?May 2023 | Episode #385
item.description:
Welcome to our May 2023 wrap-up with important news from the startup scenes in Germany, Austria, and Switzerland in 30 minutes or less ????.

We follow our top-down structure in the news: First, the top news, then we look with a bird's eye view at the startup ecosystem in the German language countries, dig deeper by looking at exciting startup cities and end with general news... Feed: https://feeds.captivate.fm/deeptechgermany/
